   "title": "ISSUE_001: Notes E1527-21 became mandatory for AAI on February 13, 2024",
   "match_criteria": "PASS if the memo states or conveys that ASTM E1527-21 became the mandatory standard for All Appropriate Inquiries (AAI) compliance under 40 C.F.R. Part 312 as of February 13, 2024 (or early 2024), superseding E1527-13. FAIL if this date/fact is absent."
