   "title": "ISSUE_001: Assesses threat to BFPP defense from ASTM citation error",
   "match_criteria": "PASS if the memo analyzes that using or citing the wrong ASTM standard could jeopardize Cornerstone's CERCLA bona fide prospective purchaser (BFPP) defense because it may fail to satisfy AAI requirements. FAIL if no connection is drawn between the citation error and the BFPP defense."
