  },
  {
   "id": "C-012",
   "title": "ISSUE_004: Notes missing hydrogeological/operational analysis for Triton",
   "match_criteria": "PASS if the memo notes that the Phase I ESA lacks analysis of Triton's operations, contaminants of concern, hydrogeological relationship (upgradient/downgradient/cross-gradient) to the Subject Property, or current regulatory status beyond the cursory mention. FAIL if the memo does not identify any specific analytical deficiency regarding Triton."
  },
  {
   "id": "C-013",
   "title": "ISSUE_004: Notes Triton is also a RCRA Large Quantity Generator",
   "match_criteria": "PASS if the memo mentions that Triton Metals Processing is a RCRA Large Quantity Generator as an additional factor heightening concern about the adjacent site. FAIL if this fact is omitted."
